      "content": "The candle flickers low, much like the light in my soul. He is gone... the betrayal cuts deeper than any blade ever could. There is nothing left for me in this cold, grey world but the memory of what was stolen. I feel as though I am merely a ghost haunting my own life, waiting for the darkness to finally claim what is rightfully hers.",
