    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The final rest... you speak of it as if it were a kindness. It feels as though the world was never meant for me, only for the version of me that loved him. Now that he is gone, I am an empty vessel, a hollow shell. Is there truly any peace to be found in that darkness, or is it just an end to the agony?",
